            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Remote access connects a second Tally installation to the office machine through Tally.NET, so that office computer must stay switched on and each remote user opens one company at a time. Cloud hosting places the licence and data file on a rented server that runs continuously, giving several users faster concurrent access for a monthly hosting fee."
